{
  "stem": "18068.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mostly it was in the East End, which was full of people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we lived on the outskirts, so we didn't have many casualties.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942 came along, and the captain said, all you young blokes go and join the forces.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're no more reserves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I registered in the forces, and they said to me, what work you doing now?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, at the moment, army casualty service, which was true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got my calling up papers, Royal Army Medical Corps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I became a medic--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because I was trained.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was immaterial, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to training, three months' training [INAUDIBLE] exercises, drill and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we were allocated a unit, which was gonna be our unit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was allocated to the field ambulance, because I was A1.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you're not A1 in the army in the medical service, they put you in a hospital-- hospital work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in a field ambulance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is with the infantry, because I was trained and A1.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fit-- you're fit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's nothing wrong with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Physically and mentally fit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were doctors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Doctors.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They have the rank of an officer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Though they're [? only ?] young-- they just got their medical degree-- soon as they became of the medical service, they had a rank officer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were privates.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'd done all the spade work, but I was-- I was already trained.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You would have to go for exams in the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See, your classification in nursing service.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was-- I had no classification, [? by ?] the first exam I had was NO3, nursing orderly, class three.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As you go through the army, you take more exams.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You're upgraded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Class two, NO2.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then NO1, which is the highest.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
